  description: "The Strigoi is a dangerous troublemaker that spreads sickness and
    disease to his family and friends that they had in life. \nThey don\u2019t necessarily
    drink their victims blood, but strangles them for their own amusement. \nThe
    Strigoi is a thief and likes to steal alcohol and cured meats."
